summary:
- **Stop Loss Trigger Event**: MINI Long series (ASX Code: MINKOR) suspended due to Underlying Parcel Price (Mineral Resources Ltd) falling to/below Stop Loss Level (AUD 33.7300 per parcel).  
- **Trading & Settlement**:  
  - Temporary bid by issuer at Cash Amount from 2pm next trading day until 4pm the following day.  
  - If not sold during this window, holders receive Stop Loss Amount within 10 business days; MINIs then terminated.  

No material capital markets impact (no capital raising, financials, or valuation changes disclosed).
